16 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 24-164 of Title 70, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. Nothing in this act shall be construed to diminish or
20 infringe upon any right protected under the First Amendment to the
